Package: scploid
Title: Single Cell RNA-seq Aneuploidy Caller
Version: 0.9
Authors@R: person("Jonathan", "Griffiths", email = "jag216@cam.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: scploid is a small R package that calls aneuploid chromosomes from single-cell RNAseq data. The algorith is described in the paper "Mosaic autosomal aneuploidies are detectable from single-cell RNAseq data", for which this package was written.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
License: GPL-v3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
	reshape2,
	ggplot2
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
